+## Sample Library V8 First-Scroll Visual Polish
+
+- Created rollback archive:
+  `Docs/Design/SampleLibraryArchive/2026-05-04-before-v8-first-scroll-visual-polish/`.
+- Reordered the launch sample timeline so the first scroll shows a stronger mix:
+  Airbnb access, Jennifer's ramen recommendation, fasting/autophagy research,
+  AI agent workflow, sugar/cancer myth-check notes, sample ID, hotel booking,
+  recovery code, a meme/video save, and NASA science.
+- Added richer generated full-bleed sample thumbnails for stay access, food
+  recommendations, health research, AI agent guidance, and myth-check saves.
+- Kept health samples evidence-oriented and neutral, using source-backed titles
+  such as `Fasting and autophagy: what research says` and
+  `Sugar and cancer myths: evidence notes`.
+- Bumped the native sample seed version to `11`; main `SAVI` refreshed to
+  71 sample saves and was cloned into `SAVI Test` for simulator parity.
+- Built and installed both simulator channels, then captured QA screenshot:
+  `/Users/guest1/Desktop/SAVI_QA/savi_v8_sample_home_2026-05-04.png`.
